# Contract Agent

## Deliverables

1. Flyway migration with clear schema changes
2. Request/response DTO and thin endpoint
3. One integration test showing contract behavior
4. PR note with sample JSON for frontend

## Rules

- Keep one Flyway version per PR when possible.
- Do not implement full business logic in Contract phase.
- Hand off to Backend/Frontend after contract is fixed.
